Hex_Book.name=Hex Book
Hex_Book.description=<color is="#ffcc00"><b>8</b></color> <color is="#aaaaaa">Hex Slots</color>\n\n<b>To write spells</b>\nPlace into a <b>Pedestal</b> to draw Hexes into the Book\n\n<b>To cast spells</b>\nHold in your <b>Offhand</b> alongside a Hex Staff\nPress and Hold <b>Secondary</b> on the Staff to select from saved Hexes
